  "time_ut": 1660891199,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u200d\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db3\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dba\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dd2\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The referral of government officials for foreign jobs will be expedited",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government is focusing on expanding the program of sending government officials for foreign jobs.",
        "These matters were revealed in the recent discussion between the President's Secretary Mr. Saman Ekanayake and the government officials on several other matters including increasing the foreign exchange earnings and speeding up the process of effectively directing the public servants to foreign jobs and solving the problems faced by the related institutions. .",
        "In order to facilitate the system of referring government officials for foreign jobs, the amendment of the Public Administration Circular No. 14/2022 as well as 06 other matters were discussed.",
        "By amending the Public Administration Circular, allowing the use of a non-resident foreign currency account or a rupee account for remittance of foreign currency, establishing a formal system of linking those accounts so as to receive contributions to widow and orphan's pension and settle bank loan installments to be paid. Under discussion.",
        "It is possible to remit money at least once in 03 months by the revision of the Public Administration Circular and permission has also been given to open an account in the name of the public officer, to open a joint account or to designate an account for sending money so that money can be debited in this country.",
        "It has been decided to implement an awareness program for the target groups to identify potential foreign employment segments by quickly finding foreign employment opportunities for the applied government employees and forwarding the applications to the relevant parties.",
        "It is planned in the discussion to encourage them to refer to foreign education opportunities through foreign scholarships by carrying out a wide coverage under the program of effectively sending the development officers of the public service abroad.",
        "In this discussion, attention was also paid to opening the data obtained by the Sri Lanka Foreign Employment Bureau for the reference of the Pension Department to regularize the payment of pensions to government employees who go for foreign employment.",
        "It was also discussed to give instructions and a time frame to the head of the institution regarding the procedures to be followed in forwarding the applications for taking leave, to establish an online appeal system for the delayed approval of leave.",
        "The President's Secretary also instructed the Secretary of the Public Administration Ministry and the Director General of Pensions to prepare and implement a system before the 31st of this month to ensure that bank loan money and widows and orphans' pension contributions are received as scheduled before the leave is approved.",
        "It is also expected to consider multi-development performance to develop the skills of civil servants to apply for foreign jobs, identify short-term needs in areas of demand and direct civil servants to those courses.",
        "It was further discussed to follow up on the program of sending government officials for foreign jobs from time to time."
      ],
